cripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/mark/5.34-36?lang=eng#p34\">Mark 5:34 (34–36)</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"10\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note10a\" data-full-marker=\"10a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128356203\" id=\"note10a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"tg\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/tg/steadfastness?lang=eng\"><small>TG</small> Steadfastness</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"11\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note11a\" data-full-marker=\"11a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128356205\" id=\"note11a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/deut/11.8-9?lang=eng#p9\">Deut. 11:9 (8–9)</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/9.16?lang=eng#p16\">Alma 9:16</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note11b\" data-full-marker=\"11b\">\n<p data-aid=\"128356207\" id=\"note11b_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/hel/8.19?lang=eng#p19\">Hel. 8:19</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/10.16?lang=eng#p16\">3 Ne. 10:16</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note11c\" data-full-marker=\"11c\">\n<p data-aid=\"128356209\" id=\"note11c_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/morm/5.9,12?lang=eng#p12\">Morm. 5:12 (9, 12)</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/morm/7.1?lang=eng#p1\">7:1</a>.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"12\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note12a\" data-full-marker=\"12a\">\n<p data-aid=\"128356211\" id=\"note12a_p1\"><span data-note-category=\"cross-ref\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/enos/1.12-13?lang=eng#p13\">Enos 1:13 (12–13)</a>.</span></p>\n</li